N'echiche ndï ''traditional'' Igbo, Chukwu bụ eze ndï chi na ndï uwa. Aha ya nwe "chi" la "ukwu". Chukwu bụ onye mere he lile (chi- n'eke). Nkea bụ nke ana-kpo ya ''[[Chineke]]'' ugbua. Chukwu abughi nwoke, abughi nwinye. Mgbe ndï bekee bïara, nwe kporo Chukwu chi nke ndi Christian, me ya nke nwoke.

Nkea bụ nke ndï Igbo nnuku bụ Christians ugbua.

